GET http://localhost:3001/api/debug/stations


### Login failure - wrong password
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "wrong"
}


### Login success
POST http://localhost:3001/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}


### Current session after login
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current


### Logout
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current


### Current session after logout
GET http://localhost:3001/api/sessions/current

